diamond on top. instead of coming down to the a sharp point, it is a bit like there is a neck.

if this is a body, there is a diamond head with both arms up. the right arm is slightly higher than the left. the 'body' is short of a right angled parallelogram
diamond head upright. neck is not a sharp defined angled, body is mostly straight then angled. right arm is extended straight and then angled downward into the body
the body is almost zig zag
diamond head on top, on the left side of the box. standing on one leg, with the other leg extended out to the right.
almost like there is a tail on the end of the extended leg
mostly blocked body. diamond head on top. sharp point at the end. into a straight line of shoulders. slightly jagged on the right side of the body, several angles

looks more like a piece of art than a body. this one has a diamond head that is angled to the left. it has appendages off to the right and an angled extension to the left.

okay, this looks like an animal to me. larger body. two legs and feet are visible. diamond is not on top exactly, but angled off to the right. there is a sharp point on the body at the top that comes down into a angled shape and a large body. but to me, it looks like a large animal
one foot is on the ground, one in the air. both facing left

this looks like machinery to me. like a funnel of some sort. square/diamond at the top with a triangle off to the right. straight line attached to square/diamond with straight right line that angles down into a large shape. the bottom is not quite a straight line, but it is the widest length shape.

looks like a waiter or someone getting a diploma to me. diamond head on top extending into a body. straight line on the bottom. extended out to the left, straight line on top, angled down and sort of a square below
half of a windmill at top. two angled triangles at the top going down into a diamond/square, then it goes into a large, misshapen triangle

diamond/square towards the top, but angled left, attached to a straight line on a diagonal. bottom is flat angles up. triangle on the right side extended but attached to the shape
diamond head into a large black shape. downward sloping shoulders on both sides, straight lines on both sides, extension out to the right side, short flat bottom

person with arms up. diamond head slightly to the left. right arm higher than the left. parallelogram body shape
repeat of leg extension. facing left, leg extension to the right, ending with a triangle that resembles a tail. diamond head on top left side, arms triangle arms extending towards the left as well
art piece again. split triangles on the top extending into a square/diamond, then into a large misshapen triangle.
diamond head on top into a straight flat line. flat line on left side,jagged edge on right side. mostly a misshapen block body with angles on the right side
diamond on top. sort of looks like someone kneeling or a dog kneeling. diamond on top, facing right. arm extension to the right.
zig zag body at the bottom. diamond head on top, facing right, straight arm extension on the right, angled legs on the right as well
one that looks like a big animal again. big body. two legs, facing left, one leg on the ground, one in the air. diamond angled to the right on the 'back' of the animal
person sitting on the floor again. diamond head facing left and slightly angled down. legs extended to the left, bent knee. mostly straight back on the right side.

diamond on top, but sharply angled to the left extending to a straight angled line, a bit of a funnel on the back of it, rather than a complete triangle. shapes on the bottom, angled, triangle on the right side towards the bottom. triangle is facing down.
looks more like a modern art piece than a person
